metadata.name: Iron City of Dis
metadata.description:
The walls, buildings, and other structures clutter the immense black metropolis and glow at the edges like heated glass. The city is a broken maze of metal ramparts built into miles of steep hillsides and shattered towers framing an endless labyrinth of twisting alleyways.

Mixed media, paper, acrylic, and oil + digital
Original File is 7421 x 6848 px 300 dpi
